  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Handyman",
  "description": "<p><strong>KEY RESPONSIBILITIES AND ACCOUNTABILITES</strong></p><ul><li>Perform preventive and corrective maintenance of facilities and equipment.</li><li>Repair of mobile medical equipment (wheelchairs, shower trolleys, etc.) and other equipment/furniture.</li><li>Perform electrical works (laying of cables, etc.).</li><li>Perform plumbing works inclusive of clearing of chokes.</li><li>Assist in painting.</li><li>Assist in logistical set-up for events held at the Home.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Certificate in Electrical / Mechanical / Air-conditioning / Building Services / Engineering</li><li>At least 3 to 5 years of hands-on experience</li><li>Knowledge and experience in M&E works are required</li><li>Experience in mobile medical equipment (wheelchairs, shower trolleys, etc.) maintenance is an added advantage</li><li>Able to use the digital Work Order Management System</li><li>Able to handle heavy loads (more than 30kg)</li><li>On the job training will be provided</li></ul>",
